{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}About Us{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <div data-controller="aos">
        <section class="flex justify-center bg-white dark:bg-orange-400/10" style="background: url({{ asset('images/martian_landscape.webp') }}) center center no-repeat; background-size: cover;">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-(--breakpoint-xl) px-4 py-8 sm:py-12 lg:px-6">
                <div class="mb-10 max-w-(--breakpoint-md) dark:text-white sm:text-base" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800">
                    <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl tracking-tight">About Us</h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        At {{ domain|title }}, we’re not just imagining life on Mars—we’re building the tools to make it happen!
                        This project is a fun, tech-driven showcase of what modern web technologies (and a little creativity) can achieve.
                        While you won’t find any actual Martian supplies for sale, you will find a fully functional, streamlined e-commerce backend that demonstrates the true power of modern PHP.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        PHP has evolved into a type-safe, efficient, and robust powerhouse.
                        It simplifies development, reduces maintenance costs, and unlike constantly shifting JavaScript frameworks, keeps your codebase stable without endless refactoring.
                     </p>
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        With over 20 years of e-commerce experience, the creator of this project has been involved in every aspect of building and scaling online businesses.
                        From working directly with customers to leading development teams and scaling startups into thriving enterprises, this project is a testament to a career dedicated to innovation and real-world problem-solving.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-10 max-w-(--breakpoint-md) dark:text-white" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl">Built on Modern, Reliable Technologies</h3>
                    <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-1">
                        <li>PHP 8 and Symfony for a robust, reliable back-end architecture</li>
                        <li>Hotwire Turbo for seamless server-side rendering and fast navigation</li>
                        <li>Tailwind CSS for fast, responsive design</li>
                        <li>Amazon EC2/RDS/S3 for scalable hosting and storage</li>
                        <li>AI-Generated Content: Unique products and images created by AI</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-10 max-w-(--breakpoint-md) dark:text-white sm:text-base" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl">A Feature-Rich, Fun E-Commerce Demo</h3>
                    <p>
                        {{ domain|title }} provides a comprehensive suite of e-commerce back-end tools, with product management, supplier integration, dynamic pricing models, order processing, all powered by real-time simulations of customer orders and supplier interactions.
                        With built-in sales reporting and data visualizations, this project explores the future of e-commerce - on Earth or Mars!
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4 flex items-center justify-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400" data-aos-duration="800">
                    <twig:Button
                        tag="a"
                        href="mailto:adamashmore@me.com"
                        class="flex items-center font-bold space-x-1"
                        variant="secondary"
                    >
                        <span>Contact Us</span>
                    </twig:Button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
{% endblock %}